   ],
   "source": [
    "\"\"\"Cell 8: [FUTURE] Fortify Pre-calculated Set.\n",
    "\n",
    "This cell is a placeholder for future work on improving the robustness and\n",
    "effectiveness of the trusted reference set. The ideas below can be explored\n",
    "to strengthen the defense — when ready, apply them to `trusted_feats` and\n",
    "re-run Cell 7 to recompute the whitening stats.\n",
    "\"\"\"\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Cell 8: Fortification placeholder — no modifications applied.\")"
   ]
